  {
    "type": "EXPOSITORY (ENGLISH BIBLE)",
    "name": "Benson Commentary",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "Genesis 2:23",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Genesis 2:23",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "This is now bone of my bone — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Probably it was revealed to Adam in a vision, when he was asleep that this lovely creature, now presented to him, was a piece of himself, and was to be ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "his companion, and the wife of his covenant. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "In token of his acceptance of her, he gave her a name, not peculiar to her, but common to her sex: she shall be called ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "woman, isha, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "a ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "she-man, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "differing from man in sex only, not in nature; made ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "of man, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "and joined ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "to man.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "",
        "children": []
      }
    ]
